  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd : \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I also accept the request of the youth to be allowed to engage in protests in a peaceful manner: President",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Everyone is allowed to engage in peaceful protests as per the law of the land. President Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that he will accept the change in the system of government which was seen as the demand of the youth involved in the protest.",
        "The President said this during a discussion held yesterday (27) at Sirikotta, the headquarters of the United National Party in Purakottai.",
        "The demand of the protesting youth was to change the system of government in the country. President Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that he also accepts it.",
        "United National Party General Secretary Palita Range Bandara, National Organizer Sagala Ratnayake and Party Chief Executive Officer Shamal Senarath welcomed the President who visited the party headquarters.",
        "The President further mentioned that according to the law of the country, everyone is allowed to engage in protests in a peaceful manner, and those who participated in the protest have the same right and he saw that youths with various talents participated in it.",
        "The President said that he took office when the country was in a very difficult situation and said that he has taken many steps to overcome the economic challenge and take the country forward."
      ],
